author: Palak  Agrawal

text:
Okay, was waiting for your 10 minutes to get over, and decided to write a serious one for you. You were probably one of the greatest friend I got after coming back to campus for that month.  I don't have a lot of memories with you, but jo hai wo kaafi jyada amazing hai. That see-saw, I don't know tere liye jyada embarassing tha yaa mere liye, lol. L-19(blurrrrrrrrrðŸ˜‚), that amazing mama-mio wala mojito, and that GH terrace (I wanna know Anchal ko uss din terrace pe chuhiya itni jldi kaise guess kiya tha, lol), it was all precious. 

Tbh, I have 2 split personality of yours with me. One Singh I used to casually know, and the other Tindal, I got to know a few weeks back, and wo dono bohot jyada split personalities hai (dm me for more details). I wish baad waali Tindal personality thoda pehle notice ki hoti, or bhi kaafi fun hota campus me, lol. Anyway, apne Bangalore ke plans yaad rakhna, and trip to hai hi teri sponsored. Hope to meet you super soon uncle. Just be the sane singh that you are. Hopefully ye co-headship abhi lambi chalegi, and also people like you are rare to find, so I am not loosing you that easily.

P.S. I still have that secret of yoursðŸ˜‚

author: Palak  Agrawal

text:
Aaj likhne ka kaafi mood bana hai, to thoda lamba or senti jaayega, padhke to tune khush hi hona hai madarchod, tu hi bolti hai naa jyada expressive nahi hu me, pehli or aakhiri baar express kr rhi, to khush ho jaana pdhke, iske baad nhi hone waala ye. One of the best things jo IITK ne mjhe diya hai wo tu hai (sounding like Nareda I know, but chill hai). Yaad hoga tjhe kaisi masoom si, bholi bhaali aayi thi me, mjhe jo itna frank kiya hai logo se, sikhaya ki dost duniya itni achi nhi hai jitni tum samajhti ho, duniya madarchod hai. Har ek cheez me mjhe support kiya, rules todhne sikhaye (sbse epic ESC201 tha), mere itne jyada saare randi rone sune har time, gaaliyan bhi di hai sunne ke baad, but har cheez ka solution nikal jaata tha yrr tjhse baat krke. Ek point tha meri har problem ka solution tu thi, fir ek point aaya (pata hi hoga kyu aaya), jab , meri sbse badi problem hi tu thi. Behenchod, agar kisi insaan ki wajah se me zindagi me kabhi royi hungi naa to wo tu hai. Behechod, bolti hai ki JD or tum ekdum similar ho, to ye nhi samajh aaya tjhe ki wo rota hai itna, to ho sakta hai me bhi roti hu. Mtlb me close nhi hoti logon se jyada, pata hi hai tjhe, but pata nhi terese hu. Wahan Shimla me literally meri feelings ye thi ki yaar sahi me bohot sahi tha pehle ki kisise bhi close nhi thi, kyuki end me to sbko chhodna hi hota hai, ye bhi chhod hi di naa (firse Nareda waali feel). But thike, mtlb mjhe pata hai me tere liye kaafi important hu, but bc banda aane ke baad sab badal jaate hai, tum bhi koi exception nhi thi. Or agar campus me mjhe sbse jyada nafrat ek insaan se hai to wo hai JD, but baat ye hai ki uski jyada koi glti nhi hai usme. Shimla waali trip bohot hi jyada bekaar thi, wahan pe pata nhi hoga 2 raat me bhi kaafi royi thi, but hamesha ki tarah tu thi nhi sambhalne ko, kyuki pati bhi tha naa tumhare paas to, or fir uske baad jab time bacha to tumne Karan ko pakad liya, jisse hume realise hua ki tumhare liye life me aage badhna or doosre log dhoondna bohot aasan hai (another instance jab tune abhi campus me kaha tha ki me nhi aa rhi hall, mjhe hall-9 me patte khelne me bohot majja aa rha hai), but JD or mere jaise logo ke liye nhi hai, yaad rakhna isse. Khair, dost shukriya humare jeevan me aane ke liye, humko sudharne ke liye, Tindal jaise logon ko judge krne me humari help krne ke liye, or hume humare ye upar likhe hue jaise faaltu ke randi rone sunke unko suljhaane ke liye. Me jaanti hu bohot saare logon ko campus me, but dil ka connect sirf tere saath hai, chuhiya, Thanya kisike saath nhi hai. Itni connected bachpan se aaj tak apne gharwaalo ke alawa shayad nhi hongi kisise bhi. Lekin behenchod isiliye connect nhi hoti me, kyuki fir uss insaan se related faaltu ki baaton pe bohot jyada sochne lag jaati hu me, or ye khaaali hone ka asar nhi hai agar tjhe wo lag raha hai to. Agar me bohot jyada hi busy hoti naa to bhi mjhe tere ye last 1 mahine ke ignorance se shayad utna hi farak padta. Bas bhadas thi nikaal di, feel mat krna jyada warna ro dogi. Achi insaan ho yrr tum, bas exclusice raho humare liye, sbke paas jaa jaake unki dikkatein naa suljhaya karo, I feel jealous (ye nhi btaya maine shayad tjhe kabhi pehle). PLease meri life se jaana mat kabhi bhi. Baaki to me nhi jaane dungi, bas JD ki baat aati hai to me fir piche ho jaati hu. Wahan tjhe hi sambhalna pdega. BC pdhte pdhte gaaliyan de rhi hogi ki ek rone waala kam tha kya jo isne bhi shuru kr diye, but thike mummy se nhi royenge to kisse royenge, or hum thodi roj roj rote hai. 

BC bas visible mat krna isko, acha sa gaaliyon bhara likhenge tumhara visible karane le liye.

text:
Yo Aishwarya!!
Yaar bohot bakchodi kiye hai saath me. Drameve1 ke baad to jyada contact nhi tha, but bhai Antaragni kaafi jyada fun. Har roj hall-1 ke kisi room pe baithe hote the, or next kya yaar bhook lag rhi hai, chalo canteen chalte hai. But core team se baat kon krwayega wahan pahuchke, tum karo yrr ladki ho mana nhi krenge wo log. And sbse epic, yaar vasul ke jaayenge poora yahan se, hahaha. Baaki mtlb itne ache se summarise kiya hai naa tune mere memoir pe, icha kr rhi wahi copy-paste maar du (doosre memoir me krti hu). Bas yrr koi photo nhi hai saath me uss time ki, regret rahega wo hamesha. Kisi bhi participant ki koi dikkat hoti thi, I was like thike naa yrr koi ni dekh lenge, but tu poori headache apne sur leke kaam krta tha. Day3 nhi bhool sakte kabhi bhi, BC mote ne kya confuse krke rakha hua tha, 3 baar scheduling krwayi thi, fir bhi chod hue the agle din. Baaki Ratnesh ki lene me aaj bhi utna hi fun aata hai, or ye topic hamesha common rhega jab bhi milenge (sorry Ratnesh, agar tu ye pad raha hai to). Best decision tha Shivam ka jo tjhe Nationals ka manager nhi banaya tha, warna itni bakchodi shayad naa ho paati, hehe. Anyway, aise hi humesha bakchod or bindass rehna. Kabhi milte hai wapas. Take Care!!

text:

From Anjan Srivastava ka "Us ladki do samjha dijiye" to Ratnesh ka "Mai meditate karne jaa raha" kaafi majja bhai. Kaafi zyaada chapu time spend kiye hai tumhare saath chahe wo Hall-1 ho, events ground ya L-7.
Bakchodi kayam rakhna, Umeed hai phir milenge.

author: Palak  Agrawal

text:
PR calling Festi!!
Yaar teri first memory naa 1st year ki hai, jab tu Katiyar ke liye birthday card banane GH ayaa tha, lol (Am I allowed to openly say this?). Hamesha ye discussion kaafi hota tha humara ki kaafi similar ho tum dono, literal bhai lagte ho. 
Anyway, uske baad Antaragni'19 ke baad ig diwali ke baad call aata hai tera, bro milna hai kuch gadbad ho gyi. BC bhand hoke chhoti ko bata diya tha tune, meri fati nhi thi, but jis tareeke se tu express kr rha tha, aisa lag rha tha ki fatni chahiye. Uske baad to yrr fir CORE TEAM, alag feels, alag expectations, or kaafi jyada enthu. Enthu to ussi se yaad aata hai jo "KAIROS" naam pe kitna jyada discussion hua tha, lol. But, ek point aane ke baad, enthu kaafi down ho gaya tha. Tune or Shrey ne hi milke sambhala tha poora, placements ke baad sbko jinda kiya, or fir karali BC (wo feel nhi hai, but apni Antargni thi yrr). Bohot jyada miss kiya maine, jo hall-12 me saath milke kaam or bakchodi ki hai tum logo ne (photos or videos aa rhi thi mere paas regularly), or jo final night bhand hue ho tum log. Goa trip jldi plan karo yrr, saath me bhand hona hai BC (OAT ki tarah nhi hopefully).  Dukh kaafi raehga on-ground Antaragni naa hone ka, jitna expected tha utni bond nhi ho paayi me team me, but at the end kya hi kar sakte hai.  Khair kaafi BT hai meri udhar, Tindal ke saamne nahi nikali kabhi, tere saamne pata nhi kyu nikal rhi. Anyways, umeed hai Goa me jld hi milenge. Tab tak Take Care, or apna enthu or feel humesha aisi hi rakhna!!

Bhai tere saath Somesh ko galiyaane me kaafi jyada majjaa aata hai, dil se nikalti hai uske liye to gaaliyan. Manali trip to kaise hi bhool sakte hai. Kaafi sexy trip thi wo. Bas ye corona hate, next trip pakka Ladakh ki hai. Guide se setting krke aaye hi the hall-13 me aane se pehle. Jald hi milte hai. Tab tak apne HR ko jyada mat tang krna, BC nikaal dega, lol. But uske baad bhai Hall-1 ka quarantine, kaafi fun bhai. Bohot majja aaya tha, but bc jldi so jaati thi tu, warna or majje krte.
I don't think I have ever told you this, but I admire your strength. Maybe I haven't helped you a lot in your elections (sahi me door rehna tha yrr mjhe unn sabse), but I always respected you for being so brave and fearless, and for always standing up for what you believed. Respect man.
Ye nhi pata chala mjhe aaj take bas ki tu intni jldi ghar kyu chali gyi thi quarantine ke baad? Humari wing ko quarantine se to nikalne deti atleast, fir judge krti naa campus ka environment. Baaki birthday ka hall-10 wala ritual, hopefully agar aap Bangalore aayi to continue rahega. Aa jana naa yrr, jo hall-1 me daaru peeni reh gyi thi, wo bhi to peeni hai (you know I have experiences now, lol). Bas randi rone mat krna peene ke baad (jo tune bataya tha tu krti hai generally, lol). Mast naachenge bhand hoke. Hope to see you soon dost!! Take care!! <3

Baaki yaar, last night daaru jugaadne ke liye kaafi thanks, bohot fun night thi wo, kaafi majja aaya tha. Tumko  dance krne ke liye bola to bas bhagne lag jaati thi, hehe. Khair, chhodo kal ki baatein , kal ki baat purani. Kabhi bhagwan ne chaaha to fir mulakaat hogi. Tab tak ke liye take care!!

text:
Dekha aaj hi daanta tune, or aaj hi memoir aa gya, lol. But yrr, kya karu jab tak deadline ekdum sur pe nhi aa jaati naa kuch kaam ho nhi paata hai. Lekin chalo aapke liye aaj ache se mood banake likh dete hai.
Yaar terese jo sbse badi shikayat hai wo ye hai ki tu bohot jyada patli hai. Tere saath sahi me photo khichana acha nhi lagta mjhe, bc complex ho jaata hai, hehe. Baaki yrr kuch bhi chahiye ho pata hota hai Manisha ke room pe milega. Kaafi kum baar hi aisa hua hoga ki tere room pe paani peene aao, kuch khaane aao, yaa kuch bhi lene aao naa mila ho. Room pe to chhodo, hall-13 ki canteen me bhi kuch chahiye ho to inn madam ke paas sab milega. Baaki poori wing me savage to bas ek tu or me hi the, hahahaha. Bhai hapan dono ek team me ho jaayein to fir, koi ni aa sakta saamne, especially Chitranshi, hehe. Baaki sab kr rhe to room ki bhi tareef kr hi deti hu teri. Wo wall yrr, itni jyada sexy, mtlb jab paint kr rhi thi naa tabhi majja aa gya tha dekhke. Baaki yrr kaafi mehnati hai tu, mtlb meri sahi me dil se icha hai ki tu creative field me kuch kar. Kaafi jyada hi chaapti ho dost tum uss field me. Haan, ek baat or tera wo class ke time laash ke jaise sona hamesha yaad rhega. Mtlb madam raat ko bolke so rhi ki please yrr subah bohot important class hai, koi jage to please jaga dena. Subah room pe jao, gala phat jaaye insaan ka chillate chillate, isko bed se uthake neeche phenkdo, chaahe kuch krlo, majaal hai jo agar madam ki icha nhi hai to uth jaaye wo, lolololol (laptop me emoji nhi aa rhe, to aise hi expressions dikhaane pad rhe, hehe). 
Kaafi jyada lamba ho gaya yrr, chalo kuch yaad aaya or to ek or me likh denge. Teri Udaipur ki trip baaki hai ek, aana kabhi. Baaki milte rehna, or haan bina mask ke bahar mat nikalna, lol (kuch nhi bas yuhi bakchodi). Take care!! <3

P.P.S.: Tu humare wing ki Godmother thi hai or humesha rahegi
P.P.P.S.: Tjhe pata nhi hai par tu hai
